  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, the detection of the feigning weakness in grip strength is measured using
      different grip strength testing instruments. Patients with injury of the upper limb are
      compared to patients with injury of the lower limb as well as healthy controls.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
